Release Notes:  RAP v4.0.3


v4.0.3 - released July 8, 2019
* Crisis fix to RAP update_bc code after FV3GFS implementation
   * Modified the update bc code to handle the FV3GFS output
   * New code runs successfully with several cases where the operational RAP failed


* Repository Details
   * After cloning the master branch of the EMC_rap git repository using the command below, retrieve the new code from the rap.v4 directory.
      * git clone https://${USER}@vlab.ncep.noaa.gov/code-review/a/EMC_rap
      * git clone ssh://${USER}@vlab.ncep.noaa.gov:29418/EMC_rap
   * The build script is located here: rap.v4/sorc/build_rap_all.sh
   * To build the code, run build_rap_all.sh and specify which codes you would like compiled within the script ("yes" or "no" switches).


* parm and sorc files changed
   * parm/rap_update_bc_parame.in
   * sorc/rap_update_bc.fd (retrieve entire directory)


* revised executables
   * rap_update_bc

    
* implementation instructions
   * Retrieve the new parm and sorc files 
   * Recompile the update_bc code

